msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:35
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_ENCOUNTER_REBEL_AVALI\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"The Rebel ship at this beacon hails, \"Finally, a break from grinding those "
"bird freaks into paste. I much prefer federation filth!\""

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:36
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_ENCOUNTER_REBEL_AVALI\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"Almost as soon as your ship slows to sublight, you receive a hail from a "
"Rebel ship. \"You're the merc that the feds hired! I thought I was stuck in "
"this awful sector forever, time to score a promotion!\""

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:38
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_ENCOUNTER_REBEL_AVALI\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"By the time you notice the Rebel ship behind the beacon, it's too late to "
"avoid a fight."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:39
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_ENCOUNTER_REBEL_AVALI\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"A Rebel ship hails. \"We did not fight a war to let a single Federation ship"
" shatter our dreams of a better galaxy!\" He locks weapons."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:40
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_ENCOUNTER_REBEL_AVALI\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"A Rebel ship approaches cautiously. \"Personally,\" says the captain, \"I'd "
"have stuck with the Federation. But I'm a soldier, sir, and I'm no use "
"without a war to fight. Raise your shields!\""

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:41
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_ENCOUNTER_REBEL_AVALI\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"You're hailed by a Rebel ship: \"When the rebellion is complete you'll see "
"the safer world we provide. Well, you won't, but you get the point.\" They "
"arm weapons."

