#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:185
msgid "data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"When you jump to this beacon, you are imediately greeted by two ships at a "
"standstill. On your left, a Multiverse Renegade of Engineer design with "
"major hull damage sits with its weapons powered. On the other side, an "
"Illuminant vessel waits with drones powered. Upon your entrance to the "
"beacon, they both hail you at the same time."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:187
msgid "data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Listen."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:189
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Engineer ship is the first to speak. An Engineer with a helmet inscribed"
" with the letter M appears on the screen and begins explaining himself. "
"\"Hey, you're a Federation vessel, right? These Avalis are selling an "
"unliscensed medication to the civilians. You need to stop them! These pills "
"have unnatural side effects, like nothing I've ever seen! Please destroy "
"them before the pills--\" The Illuminant cuts him off. \"Hey, shut up! I "
"have all the liscensing i need to sell my medication! And it's not like the "
"side effects are hidden, it's right there on the label!\" Both ships go "
"silent, waiting for you to pick a side."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:202
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Side with the Avali Elite."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:204
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Avali is delighted upon your support. \"Wow, thanks! I'll give you a "
"free sample after this if you beat him. Uh, watch out--\" The Illuminant is "
"interrupted by the Engineer, who shouts \"Do you realize how many innocent "
"civilians you're poisoning?\" before charging his weapons."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:207
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:213
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Mute them both and do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:215
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "You have *far* better things to be doing."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:217
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something on-board the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:221
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:229
msgid "data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Nope, not dealing with this."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:231
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "You have much better things to be doing."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:233
msgid ""
