msgstr "Do something on-board the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:237
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:254
msgid "data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"DESTROYED_ENGINEER_RENEGADE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"One last explosion marks the engineer's fate, as his ship breaks apart. You "
"quickly collect what remains."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:257
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"DESTROYED_ENGINEER_RENEGADE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Contact the Avali."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:263
msgid "data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"DEAD_CREW_ENGINEER_RENEGADE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The mighty cruiser vessel's engines stutter to a halt, as the last lifeform "
"reading fades away. While scrapping the hull, you find a functional drone "
"schematic, it may have failed its old master, but hopefully it'll serve you "
"better."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:267
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"DEAD_CREW_ENGINEER_RENEGADE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Contact the Avali."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:273
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT_CONTACT_ILLUMINANT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Illuminant hails you: \"Thanks for the help, I would've been toast if I "
"had to fight him any longer. Here, a sample of the medicine I was selling, "
"as a sign of my appreciation!\" Upon reading the label, you are sickened to "
"discover the side effects of these pills include \"Turning into Avali\". Did"
" you pick the right side here...?"

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:275
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT_CONTACT_ILLUMINANT\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Accept."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:277
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT_CONTACT_ILLUMINANT\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Illuminant transfers the pills to you, and gives you a friendly wave "
"before jumping away. (event unfinished, no pills yet, take consolation "
"prize)"

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:282
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT_CONTACT_ILLUMINANT\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "No, these are awful."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:284
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT_CONTACT_ILLUMINANT\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Oh, really? Well, if you aren't taking them, I guess you're just a "
"traveller. But... if you're a traveller, that means you can take me to more "
"sectors to sell my medication!\" Before you can protest, the Illuminant is "
"already abandoning her ship to join your crew."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:285
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"AVALI_ARGUMENT_CONTACT_ILLUMINANT\"]/choice[2]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Robin"

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:291
msgid "data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"INSTANT_ISSUES\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You're hailed by a Federation Autoship trying to sell you insta-noodles... "
"It's strange, considering the fact that the auto-ship seems to be of a "
"military type. It's also malfunctioning, seemingly trying to power up "
"weapons."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:294
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"INSTANT_ISSUES\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_PROTOGEN\"]/text"
msgstr "(Protogen Crew) Have your protogen fix the Autoship."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:296
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"INSTANT_ISSUES\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_PROTOGEN\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your Protogen manages to fix the malfunctioning Autoship and makes it "
"dispense Noodle Rations everywhere. It also allows you to access its store "
"interface."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:302
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"INSTANT_ISSUES\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_RSA\"]/text"
msgstr "(RSA Crew) Have your RSA crew fix the auto-ship."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:304
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"INSTANT_ISSUES\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_RSA\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your RSA member uses their years of experience to fix the malfunctioning "
"Autoship and makes it dispense Noodle Rations everywhere. It also allows you"
" to access its store interface."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:310
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"INSTANT_ISSUES\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGI\"]/text"
msgstr "(Engi Crew) Have your Engi crew fix the auto-ship."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:312
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"INSTANT_ISSUES\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGI\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your Engi fixes the malfunctioning Autoship with ease and makes it dispense "
"Noodle Rations. It also allows you to access its store interface."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:318
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"INSTANT_ISSUES\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_AVALI\"]/text"
msgstr "(Avali Crew) Have your Avali crew fix the auto-ship."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:320
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"INSTANT_ISSUES\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_AVALI\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your Avali explains that they have seen an automated merchant like this "
"before and tries to fix the malfunctioning Autoship. It didn't exactly work,"
" though..."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:325
msgid "data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"INSTANT_ISSUES\"]/choice[5]/text"
msgstr "Try to fix the auto-ship."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:327
msgid ""
"data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"INSTANT_ISSUES\"]/choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The auto-ship dispenses several piles of noodle rations before self-"
"destructing. You're still not sure what happened, but at least you can loot "
"the broken Autoship..."

#: src-en/data/events_avali.xml:333
msgid "data/events_avali.xml$//event[@name=\"INSTANT_ISSUES\"]/choice[6]/text"
msgstr "Ignore the Autoship."
